# Modern Hub Panel UI

When building or redesigning dashboard tabs (Documents, Payroll, Training, etc.), follow **`docs/MODERN_HUB_PANEL_UI_GUIDE.md`**.

## Must match Documents / Payroll hub

- Gray canvas on parent: `.card-content--{tab}` → `#f3f4f6`
- White cards, `border-radius: 10px`, subtle shadow, `1px #e5e7eb` borders
- Primary CTA: forest green `#166534` (`--hub-green` / `--dh-green`)
- Page flow: **header → 4 stat cards → filter bar → action-required banner → main + 300px sidebar**
- Grouped **collapsible sections** with unique `theme` per section (accent border, icon tile, pill tags)
- Section progress when applicable (`n/m complete`)
- Logic in `*UiHelpers.js` + `*DisplaySections.js`; panel component is presentation-only

## Naming

- Documents: `doc-hub__` · `DocumentsHubPanel.vue`
- Payroll: `pay-hub__` · `PayrollHubPanel.vue` + `PayrollHubSection.vue`
- Training (future): `train-hub__` · `TrainingHubPanel.vue`
- Submit: `submit-hub__` · `SubmitHubPanel.vue` + `SubmitPanelTab.vue`
- My Account: `acct-hub__` · `AccountHubPanel.vue` + `MyAccountTab.vue`
- My Schedule: `sched-hub__` · `ScheduleHubPanel.vue` + `scheduleDisplayViews.js`

## Do not

- Put API calls inside hub panel components
- Hardcode section colors in templates (use config `theme` + CSS variables)
- Use a different primary button color per tab
